reviewText: i enjoy this dvd!! she put on a great show over all...i forgot how many hits she had...it's a must buy.

Great DVD, great singer
Loved her voice and music ever since I first heard her on holiday in Venezuela !!
Great buy if you love latin music !

Estan todas sus mejores canciones y el show que presenta es 100% buenisimo, se ve un poco de como es el trabajo de fondo antes del show y el equipo de trabajo que tienen muy cheveres, la coreografia muy buena.

This is an amazing video by the Queen of Merengue. It is 90 minutes of one of the best shows I have ever seen. This is a must buy for latin music lovers. By the end of the video I felt like she was a close friend. I have only one of her cd's but now I am going to buy them all. She has made a friend for life. I very really give 5 stars but I think this video is worth 10 stars.
This video is amazing...her voice, like she dance and everything she do is something espectacular. She is a Latin Diva #1. I love her...Se boto La Tañon... Buy it!

Olga Tanon is one of the best merengue singers today.  She performs her hits from the past to the present including never before release songs. The backstage footage shown was really great.  A must get video.
